  "title": "Admin Assistant | Site Project | 5.5 Days | Woodlands | 9755",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Site Project Admin Assistant</strong></p><p><strong>Industry: Mechanical Engineering / Semiconductor</strong></p><p><strong>Company Office: Lavender Street</strong><br /><strong>Working Location: Project site (Woodlands)</strong></p><p><strong>5.5 days Monday – Friday: 8.30am – 5.30pm; Saturday: 8.30am – 12pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary: $ 1,800 – $ 3,000 (Depending on experience)</strong></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>At least 1 year of administrative experience (Preferably in construction or engineering industry).</p></li><li><p>Proficient in Microsoft Office (Word, Excel, Outlook).</p></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Provide daily administrative support to the project team at the site.</p></li><li><p>Prepare and maintain documentation, filing and reports.</p></li><li><p>Handle office supply procurement and inventory control.</p></li><li><p>Assist in scheduling appointments and meetings.</p></li><li><p>Liaise with vendors, clients and internal departments.</p></li><li><p>Support daily operations to ensure smooth workflow at site.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate and arrange logistics such as air and sea shipments.</p></li><li><p>Attend weekly site meetings and take minutes of meeting.<br /></p></li></ul><p>Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755</p><p>The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
